                <h1 class="project-title">Amy Foxworthy Writing</h1>

                <p>This is a portfolio website for a writer that I did. This was a unique experience because really, how often does a writer ask you to create a website for them? I can’t say no to a fresh challenge…</p>

                <span class="view-process">View Process</span>

                <div class="slide-show">
                    <div class="swiper-container foxworthy-slides">
