                                <div class="slide-description wide">
                                    <p>To display the diversity in her writing samples, I collected them all together and determined that they fell into 3 categories: Writing samples online as downloadable files (Downloads), Articles on external websites (External), and Newsletter emails (Internal). I deemed the Newsletters internal because I felt that it was best to just recreate them with HTML as opposed to taking a screen shot.  The accordion method lets the user see potentially many samples, but also giving them the option to hide them.                     </p>
                                </div>
